<h1 id='currencies'>Currencies</h1>
<p>Currencies are provided and available to load from our system, if a currency is missing please let us know so we can add it.</p>

<p>Besides the normal (fiat) currencies we have now also added some common cryptocurrencies.</p>

<p>Note: ISO 4217 unique currency codes are used as <code>id</code> fields of currencies to simlify inclusion as related IDs in documents.</p>
<h2 id='get-all-currencies'>Get all Currencies</h2><pre class="highlight shell tab-shell"><code>curl <span class="s2">"https://api.spaceinvoices.com/v1/currencies"</span> <span class="se">\</span>
  -H <span class="s2">"Authorization: TOKEN"</span>
</code></pre><pre class="highlight javascript tab-javascript"><code></code></pre>
<blockquote>
<p>Returns:</p>
</blockquote>
