<p>This endpoint retrieves all Currencies.</p>
<h3 id='http-request'>HTTP Request</h3>
<p><code>GET https://api.spaceinvoices.com/v1/currencies</code></p>
<h3 id='http-response'>HTTP Response</h3><h4 id='arguments'>Arguments</h4>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align: right"></th>
<th></th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: right">id</td>
<td>Unique ISO 4217 currency ID of model instance</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: right">name</td>
<td>Name of Currency.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: right">symbol</td>
<td>Symbol of currency if available otherwise same as id.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: right">type</td>
<td>Type of currencie. <em>Either <code>fiat</code> or <code>crypto</code></em></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
